dzen2-based conky by fog.

Dependencies:
conky, dzen2, curl, aptitude

Copy  dzicons folder and conkyrc_dzen_mine inside .conky folder.
Rename scripts folder .scripts and copy it inside your home.
Change paths, country codes, dimensions for your screen and username/password (NOT SECURE they are in PLAIN TEXT format) for your needs. 
Make dzenbar.sh executable, put it somewhere at yout path and add it to  autostart.

Enjoy.


